Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:09.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:19.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:39.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.36,0:00:46.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:53.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:59.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.31,0:01:06.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:13.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.06,0:01:20.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:28.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:05.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Nearby War
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:21.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,That wraps up\Nthe patrol flight schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:28.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have you authorized\Nmobilization of Chor Tempest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:33.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're still flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:38.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,You said we couldn't gauge\NSimoun chemistry otherwise, Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:42.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've had enough!\NYou're amazing, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:44.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,So can we...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.38,0:02:48.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,We haven't done a Ri Majon yet.\NLet's try the Ray Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:59.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Look at Aer go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:06.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:09.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's too complicated! I'm confused!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:18.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas, focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:19.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:21.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just wait... Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:12.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is currently grounded\Nuntil its newest members arrive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:14.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Sibylla Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:18.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we don't practice,\Nit'll be tough when trouble comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:22.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then use Similes.\NAfter you've received permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:27.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer! Morinas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:35.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why'd you pray without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:38.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why'd you pray without permission?\NIt was a battle drill, not a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:43.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are you scolding us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:47.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're not even\Nthe regina of Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:52.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,The regina of our chor,\NNeviril, is indisposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:54.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, I'm stepping in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:59.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh? Don't tell me\Nthat you and Sibylla Aurea...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:02.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,...have that kind of special relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:22.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer! You forgot something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:30.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,The kiss of gratitude. After exiting\Nthe Simoun, Tempus Spatium...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:33.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I couldn't care less about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:36.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you hate doing it with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:45.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Waporif, I'm sorry. We might've\Ngotten you in trouble too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:50.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's our job to launch\NSimouns when sibyllae request it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,How cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:59.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's a child. You needn't tease her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:02.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tease? Why would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:09.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,But you know what? Flying with\Nthat girl was simply wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:22.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was amazing, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:25.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which Ri Majon\Nwere you trying before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:29.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, don't do anything like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:34.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why not? Are you all okay\Nwith the way things are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:39.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,When will they put Chor Tempest\Non duty to relieve the other chors?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:46.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,If that happens, we can go back\Nto being normal Simoun sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:50.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Offering prayers and waiting\Nfor our time to go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,The day I choose to become male.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can hardly wait, Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:07:01.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm planning to choose\Nthe male gender myself, Alty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:04.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,You all think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:07.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,That it's fine to not\Ngo into battle anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:13.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's Chor Rubor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:17.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Making a safe return\Nagain today, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:29.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,You tried to do\Nthe Ray Ri Majon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:31.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,You are a genius after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:36.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can't even do\Na simple thing like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:39.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder if this really\Nis Chor Tempest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:46.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that how you feel too, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:50.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,That it doesn't matter as long\Nas you don't go into battle anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:53.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,How could anyone want to go to war?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:57.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, we are merely...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:08:01.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,...fulfilling our duties as priestesses\Nprotecting Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:04.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then you fulfill that duty too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:10.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let me make myself clear.\NAer, you and I will never be a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:27.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm Vura of Chor Rubor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:29.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll be roommates starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:33.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that right? I'm Aer of Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:36.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're an auriga, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:40.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am too.\NSay, has that Neviril always been...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:46.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since Chor Tempest is off active duty,\Nmy chor's been split into two units...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:48.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,...doing patrol flights night and day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:52.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,We don't have the luxury\Nof lazing around like you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:54.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let me sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:09.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,I bet I can fly in a way\Nthat would satisfy even you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:10.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:12.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:29.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone's in\Nthe cafeteria at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:31.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:34.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's all right. I grabbed dinner for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:36.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:39.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,What a pain in the butt...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:42.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:44.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here, your half.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:49.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:02.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which Ri Majon first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:04.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:08.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,You must like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:11.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Silver Ri Majon... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:15.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah? That's a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:19.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if we're going to,\Nlet's do it when we find the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:21.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're going into battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:27.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we do, they won't be able\Nto ground our chor anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:34.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:47.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:55.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:11:00.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,The new recruits in Chor Caput\Nare out on patrol tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:02.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why's it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:05.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe they were attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:09.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then they've got info on the enemy.\NLet's make sure the area's secure first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:15.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just one unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:18.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm in luck. This will be my last...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:44.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,It has to be Aer!\NAnd with Rimone this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:47.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone? But that's my pair...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:49.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,She rejected me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:53.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not really\Na matter of being rejected...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:58.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Another unauthorized flight?\NI wish my chor had free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:12:02.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,This means the end of\NChor Tempest. We're going to be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:04.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Should we notify the dux?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:07.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we don't get them,\Nwe're all accountable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:10.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why don't we leave them alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:15.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they want to fly,\Nwe should let them fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:18.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,They'll be back by morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:21.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can't move\Nthe Arcus Prima right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:25.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just what kind of\Npriestess is this Aer girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:30.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,All that is certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:33.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is that she has a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:36.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,A reason for being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.43,0:12:57.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a fake...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:02.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:05.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:15.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NWe're both Simoun sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:20.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,So it's true when they say that young\Ngirls fly the Simouns in Kyuukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:30.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,The disease is eating\Naway at our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:34.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are in need of new technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:37.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,The secret of Simouns,\Nhidden by Kyuukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we can acquire that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:44.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we can bid farewell to\Ntechnology that pollutes the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:04.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I did it... I've taken a Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:08.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to retire from the military!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:12.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Glory to Shoukoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:21.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:25.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,You soldiers from Shoukoku aren't\Nprotected by Tempus Spatium!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:30.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Only priestesses who haven't gone\Nto the Spring can operate Simouns!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.56,0:14:34.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Only us, people who haven't\Ndecided on a gender yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:39.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tell me how to fly it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:43.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:24.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:27.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,We retake the Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:29.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't talk so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:34.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,He can't understand our words anyway.\NShoukoku wants the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:39.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since only Simouns fly freely through\Nthe skies. But we can't hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:40.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:47.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of my friends\Nhave gone to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:50.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one\Nin my village who hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:53.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why don't you want to go, Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:59.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I'm not sure. Whether I want\Nto become a man or stay a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:03.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you go, they say Onasia\Nchooses if you haven't decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:06.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Having someone else choose\Nis worse! No, I don't want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:10.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to make\Nmistakes in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:13.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll become the best\NSimoun sibylla of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:18.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all, as long as I fly a Simoun,\NI won't have to go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:25.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tell me, young ladies...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:29.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,How does it feel?\NNot to be a man or woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:33.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't understand, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:39.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was turned male via medicine\Nand surgery right when I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:43.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the way things\Nare done in Shoukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:46.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:48.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Being born in a female body...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:54.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and then being able to choose\Nwhether to become a man or woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:56.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,How does that feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:06.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you think that man is ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:57.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go! Fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:00.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on, fly! What's wrong, demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:02.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why won't you fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:10.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry, young ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:14.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't hand this over\Nto you. It's mine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:20.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I can just take this back,\Nmy country will usher in a new era.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:22.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,The skies will clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:27.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter what, I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:39.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like I said, you can't fly a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:43.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,His comrades might come for him.\NIn Shoukoku aircraft...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:50.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,I won't let him have it.\NHe'll never take the Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:25.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Help me get him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:27.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,We need to get back right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:35.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,He's all stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:39.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let go! Let go! Let go, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:41.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't. It'll break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:49.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure someone\Nwill come looking for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:53.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:57.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,We don't know when the enemy will\Ncome. We have to take off right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:20:02.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,And we can't ever report that we\Nnearly got captured by the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:08.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,If only these hands on\Nthe flight stick could be removed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:11.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:15.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:19.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone, you can\Ngo over there till I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:21.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Go over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:55.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:04.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:07.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone! Help me carry him, Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:10.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you awake, Rimone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:12.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:53.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess I made trouble for you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:55.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,As an apology,\Nwe'll clean it ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:59.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do that, Sibylla Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.10,0:22:00.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's fine. We want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:03.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone, if you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.38,0:22:15.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Taking on the task of\Ncleaning the Simoun themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.85,0:22:18.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're starting to recognize\Nthat they're priestesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:20.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:26.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:29.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,For getting you so dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.95,0:22:47.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.69,0:22:51.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.92,0:22:58.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.00,0:23:06.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.38,0:23:19.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:24.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.66,0:23:28.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:32.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:37.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.54,0:23:43.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.08,0:23:47.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.55,0:23:53.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.19,0:23:59.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.76,0:24:06.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.23,0:24:12.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Will Dominüra be up\Nto the task of guiding Rimone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.51,0:24:15.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.27,0:24:16.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,White Loneliness\NNext time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.27,0:24:19.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,White Loneliness\NWhite Loneliness.
